EVERY
SPECIALTY
OF
MEDICINE
THE
PATHOLOGY
OF
CYSTIC
FIBROSIS
ITS
CLINICAL
FEATURES
DIAGNOSIS
AND
TREATMENT
ARE
DISCUSSED
THE
PEDIATRICIAN
WILL
NOT
WANT
TO
ATTEMPT
TO
